  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">All our efforts focus on education, wellness, and sustainability, so in partnership with Samkelwe Senior Secondary School in Nomathamsanqa, Addo, South Africa, Universal Promise has designed a Wellness Program and an After School Program that focus on emotional, physical, and sexual health. Why is this necessary? Administrators, educators, and the student body at SSSS asked for intervention to cope with life&apos;s stressors, all exacerbated by rampant unemployment, poor healthcare, and poverty.</narrative>
  </description>
